 <italic class="italic">s</italic>) is the point intensity data, and 
 <italic class="italic">σ</italic> and φ are the exponential covariance function 
 <italic class="italic">r</italic>(
 <italic class="italic">s</italic>) parameters in Eq. (
 <xref rid="Equ1" ref-type="" class="xref">1</xref>) (Diggle et al. 
 <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR11" class="xref">2013</xref>; Taylor et al. 
 <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR66" class="xref">2013</xref>).
</p>
